All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Remote, IContractorDao, IDao<Contractor>
public class ContractorRemoteDao
extends UnicastRemoteObject
implements IContractorDao

ContractorRemoteDao is a remote (RMI) implementation of IContractorDao interface. Because it is a remote object it extends UnicastRemoteObject.
